message.body: ########, can we get sushi while we are down there? It is very important because the sushi up here is terrible

Cool. Let me know which you prefer and I'll make reservations when we get closer to the day.
Hey! What movie did we say we needed to get drunk and watch next time we were together? I don't know if we can cram it in this time around but it's driving me nuts that I can't remember
